    "content": "Body:\n[\n{\n\"dataIn\": 1096,\n\"dataOut\": 1096,\n\"smsIn\": 5,\n\"smsOut\": 5,\n\"timestamp\": \"2024-02-01T09:00:00+01:00\"\n}\n]\nJSON Params Description\ndataInSim data traffic with device as target (in Bytes)\ndataOutSim data traffic device originated (in Bytes)\nsmsInSim SMS count with device as target\nsmsOutSim SMS count device originated\ntimestampdate time of the beginning of the bucket interval (in UTC)\nError case:_\nHTTP CodeError code\nmessage\n400GENERIC_INVALID_PARAMETER_ERRORThe submitted parameter is invalid.\n403FORBIDDENForbidden request\n404CELLULAR_SUBSCRIPTION_NOT_FOUNDSubscription not found\n11. Data transformation\n11.1. Data transformation components and concepts\nYou can send data to Live Objects using two sources, a device can send data using a supported protocol (LoRa®, SMS, MQTT...) or a business application by using HTTPS or MQTTS. Each source\nis processed by one or many components. Data transformation is then relies upon:\n• the data\nenrichment process\nwhich makes the link between Live ObjectsData Message and Device Management. Data enrichment is a merge of third-party data model from device\nsource with a Live Objects\ncommon data model.\n• the\ndecoding service\nwhich process Live Objects message for handling encoded data collected from various networks.\n• the\ncustom pipeline service\nwhich process Live Objects Data Messages to perform various enrichment steps\nData journey\n1. Introduction\n2. Overview\n3. Getting started\n4. Account Management and Access Control\n5. Device and connectivity\n6. MQTT protocol\n7. LwM2M protocol\n8. Device management\n9. Devices Inventory Explorer\n10. Cellular Networks (Beta)\n11. Data transformation\n12. Devices Analytics\n13. Data analysis\n14. Message routing\n14.1. Action policy\n14.2. Triggers\n14.3. Actions\n14.4. Examples\n15. Messages data model\n16. API’s for business applications\n17. Alarming\n18. Web portal\n19. Audit Log\n20. Network metrics (Beta)\n21. Tenants management\n22. Glossary\n23. Limitations\nLive Objects - complete developer guidehttps://liveobjects.orange-business.com/doc/html/lo_manua...\n124 of 21701/03/2026 03:33\nEnrichment\nprocess\nDecoding\nser vice",
